====Usage notes====
* This adjective is mostly restricted to attributive use; predicative uses such as in “My mother is stay-at-home” do exist, but are quite rare.
* In particular, this adjective is most commonly found in the expressions {{term||stay-at-home mother}}, {{term||father}}, {{term||mom}}, {{term||dad}}, {{term||motherhood}}, and so on.

